,"tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"參考價格：雙人房淡季 NT$4,020 元"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"查房價："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.agoda.com/zh-tw/city-of-dreams-the-countdown-hotel/hotel/macau-mo.html?cid=1647692","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Agoda 優惠"}]},{"type":"text","value":"、"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.hotelscombined.com.tw/Hotel/City_of_Dreams_Macau_The_Countdown.htm?a_aid=125303","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Hotelscombined 比價"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"評價：Google 4.4 分、Agoda 8.7 分"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"酒店特色"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"酒店特色"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1 澳门上葡京"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n📍 位于澳门路氹射击路。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n🔥 特色：酒店面积超大，酒店比较新，而且房间很大。还有一个非常漂亮的大型花园，欧式宫廷建筑。三楼还有自助山，平台小花园和室内外泳池 💐"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2 永利皇宫酒店"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n📍 澳门路氹路氹体育馆大马路西 50 米。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n🔥 特色：房间够大，金碧辉煌，大堂有超跑展出，看的眼花缭乱。酒店的观光缆车住客是免排队的，晚上坐着缆车观看喷泉非常惬意。门前就有轻轨站去官也街等都很便利。🏊‍♀"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"3 澳门银河酒店"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n📍 澳门路氹城。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n🔥 特色：亚洲较大型的综合休闲度假村之一。澳门亲子酒店的天花板，个别房型还能看到天浪淘园。酒店还给小朋友送了一堆东西，画板，小拖鞋 🩴，小玩偶，洗护套装，下次来澳门一定还住银河酒店 👨‍👩‍👧‍👦"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"4 澳门新濠影汇酒店"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n📍 澳门路氹澳门路氹连贯公路。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n🔥 特色：外墙建有离地 130 米的 8 字形摩天轮「影汇之星」，连接着新濠影汇的两栋酒店大楼。有水上乐园，三丽欧主题餐厅，都是小朋友喜欢的 💼"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"5 澳门丽思卡尔顿酒店"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n📍 澳门路氹「澳门银河」综合度假城, 望德圣母湾大马路。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n🔥 特色：在银河商圈里，全套房式酒店可饱览路氹金光大道的迷人景致。吃饭购物方便，出门轻轨交通很方便。🌃"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"6 澳门新濠天地 - 摩珀斯"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n📍 澳门路氹路氹连贯公路。"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n🔥 特色：拥有 772 间客房和套房设施配套超越星级酒店标准以超卓的品味。全屋智能控制，桌子和床头柜上各有一个平板电脑，用它可以完成客房里的所有需求。30 楼是行政酒廊非常漂亮。"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"澳門-旅館資訊","depth":2,"text":"澳門-旅館資訊","children":[{"id":"澳門-5-星級酒店-匯總","depth":3,"text":"澳門 5 星級酒店 匯總"},{"id":"路氹城飯店推薦","depth":3,"text":"路氹城飯店推薦"},{"id":"酒店特色","depth":3,"text":"酒店特色"}]}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:travel:v011.md","_source":"content","_file":"travel/v011.md","_extension":"md"}